299
00:17:56.636 --> 00:17:57.436
The key

300
00:17:59.076 --> 00:18:01.316
question that remained was how does this work?

301
00:18:01.536 --> 00:18:03.506
How do we get this explicit selectivity?

302
00:18:03.546 --> 00:18:07.316
And we immediately noticed that there was no real DGRAN in

303
00:18:07.476 --> 00:18:10.336
KAT2A. There was nothing that really resembled anything we had seen

