00:18:22.116 --> 00:18:26.096
that engages the single tyrosine on a helix, really grabbing on this one

308
00:18:26.156 --> 00:18:29.916
little feature to now create this large composite interface

309
00:18:29.976 --> 00:18:31.006
and providing

310
00:18:31.016 --> 00:18:34.004
selectivity.And

